ontainer\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9b4c601\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text\":\"Aj\\u00e1nlat k\\u00e9r\\u00e9s\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.bekestemetkezes.hu\\/wordpress\\/wordpress\\/ajanlatkeres\\/\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"button_text_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"background_color\":\"#272727\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\",\"_element_custom_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":99.223},\"_flex_size\":\"none\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"button\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"5d54055\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"row\",\"flex_gap\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0,\"column\":\"0\",\"row\":\"0\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3f22779\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"50\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"494e254\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"C\\u00e9g\\u00fcnkr\\u0151l\",\"title_color\":\"#22292C\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"b671bb0\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"50\"}},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"2d5af68\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div id=\\\"h-col-19\\\" class=\\\"h-col h-col-7\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-row-14\\\" class=\\\"h-row\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-col-20\\\" class=\\\"h-col h-col-12\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-widget-17\\\" class=\\\"h-widget\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"widget_17_text\\\" class=\\\"widgetWrp widget_Text_Main\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"widget_17_text_wText\\\" class=\\\"wText\\\" style=\\\"position: relative;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Munk\\u00e1nkat t\\u00f6bb \\u00e9vtizedes tapasztalattal\\u00a0 rendelkez\\u0151, elismert temetkez\\u00e9si szakemberek seg\\u00edtik a h\\u00e1tt\\u00e9rb\\u0151l\\u00a0(polg\\u00e1ri b\\u00facs\\u00faztat\\u00f3k, kopors\\u00f3- \\u00e9s urnak\\u00e9sz\\u00edt\\u0151k, kremat\\u00f3riumok, s\\u00edrk\\u00f6ves szakemberek) \\u00edgy nyugodtan r\\u00e1nk b\\u00edzhatja elhunyt szerette m\\u00e9lt\\u00f3 temet\\u00e9s\\u00e9t, v\\u00e9gs\\u0151 b\\u00facs\\u00faj\\u00e1t. Biztos lehet benne, hogy mind szakmai, mind emberi szempontb\\u00f3l kifog\\u00e1stalan, az \\u00d6n ig\\u00e9nyeihez maxim\\u00e1lisan illeszked\\u0151 szolg\\u00e1ltat\\u00e1st ny\\u00fajtunk.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"h-row-15\\\" class=\\\"h-row\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-col-21\\\" class=\\\"h-col h-col-12\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-widget-18\\\" class=\\\"h-widget\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"widget_18_text\\\" class=\\\"widgetWrp widget_Text_Main\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"widget_18_text_wText\\\" class=\\\"wText\\\" style=\\\"position: relative;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Munkat\\u00e1rsaink szak\\u00e9rtelme mellett emp\\u00e1ti\\u00e1juk\\u00a0az, amivel a legnagyobb t\\u00e1mogat\\u00e1st ny\\u00fajtj\\u00e1k\\u00a0\\u00fcgyfeleink sz\\u00e1m\\u00e1ra. K\\u00e9szs\\u00e9ggel \\u00e1llnak rendelkez\\u00e9s\\u00fckre a legbonyolultabb\\u00a0temetkez\\u00e9ssel kapcsolatos k\\u00e9rd\\u00e9sekben is. Az ig\\u00e9nybe venni k\\u00edv\\u00e1nt szolg\\u00e1ltat\\u00e1sokkal kapcsolatban korrekt t\\u00e1j\\u00e9koztat\\u00e1st adnak, a temet\\u00e9st pedig a legnagyobb gondoss\\u00e1ggal szervezik meg, \\u00edgy \\u00d6n mindv\\u00e9gig biztos lehet benne, hogy minden rendben, a megbesz\\u00e9ltek szerint fog megt\\u00f6rt\\u00e9nni a temet\\u00e9s lebonyol\\u00edt\\u00e1sa sor\\u00e1n.<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div id=\\\"h-row-16\\\" class=\\\"h-row\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-col-22\\\" class=\\\"h-col h-col-12\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"h-widget-19\\\" class=\\\"h-widget\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"widget_19_text\\\" class=\\\"widgetWrp widget_Text_Main\\\">\\n<div id=\\\"widget_19_text_wText\\\" class=\\\"wText\\\" style=\\\"position: relative;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Koll\\u00e9g\\u00e1ink csalhatatlan \\u00edzl\\u00e9se \\u00e9s term\\u00e9kismerete garant\\u00e1lja \\u00d6nnek ig\\u00e9nyeihez \\u00e9s anyagi lehet\\u0151s\\u00e9geihez illeszked\\u0151 kegyeleti kell\\u00e9kek, szolg\\u00e1ltat\\u00e1sok kiv\\u00e1laszt\\u00e1s\\u00e1t; az eg\\u00e9sz csal\\u00e1d megnyugv\\u00e1s\\u00e1t \\u00e9s a gy\\u00e1sz feldolgoz\\u00e1s\\u00e1t el\\u0151seg\\u00edt\\u0151, m\\u00e9lt\\u00f3 b\\u00facs\\u00fa megszervez\\u00e9s\\u00e9t. Forduljon hozz\\u00e1nk bizalommal!<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"text_color\":\"#030303\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"13\",\"right\":\"13\",\"bottom\":\"13\",\"left\":\"13\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8292399\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d582d90\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Az iroda elhelyezked\\u00e9se a t\\u00e9rk\\u00e9pen\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"802004e\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"03a1931\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"address\":\"B\\u00e9k\\u00e9scsaba, Munk\\u00e1csy utca 9.\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"google_maps\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
